{"tid":304231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得香港好悲哀","createTime":"2017-06-30T17:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T21:29:36.000Z","uid":58358,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d8e134ae19a11c306c0320fea831ef26789f1b5","tid":304231,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:21:16.000Z","msg":"好似韓國，日本咁，佢地都以自己國家為榮，而我地一直只係殖民地居民，我地又無輝煌既歷史，一直都被侵略統治。由宋帝南逃喪於崖山，到殖民統治權力移交，都係令人沮喪既事迹居多。少少令人自豪既只係英治既一段光輝時期，但要拎到呢樣出黎增加我地既身份認同，實在覺得羞愧，畢竟都係被殖民統治，只係英國人同我地相處得好咁解。<br />\n<br />\n到今時今日，好多人仍然要介意自己拎咩護照，bno, bc 好型，特衰火車頭好柒，但邊有國家既人會好似我地咁? 無民族認同，國家認同，身份認同，經濟由宗主國操控，任人宰割勞役。<br />\n<br />\n我地無一個令我地願意以性命去效忠既國家，因此我地無一個重要既後盾。 我地出國同人講我地係香港人，有時要解釋一輪，香港人唔同中國人，但香港唔係一個獨立而民主既國家，人地一句就可以收我地皮。<br />\n<br />\n講起香港，到處都係恥辱。 似乎呢度既人世世代代都要咁樣生活落去，世世代代都要繼承呢啲歷史。"},{"pid":"e3263de6ee3cc67ca8148cdc3f96b0e02a3c8355","tid":304231,"uid":10692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:31:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5a39add273acc5e8e7932893bfa037b54f6b9e8","tid":304231,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:46:53.000Z","msg":"其實香港有輝煌既歷史"},{"pid":"25dac4dd1ae99ec5321337d54ae7c906defdbd53","tid":304231,"uid":48659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:47:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/all_nations/imgs/e/0/e08e7c56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fall_nations%2Fimgs%2Fe%2F0%2Fe08e7c56.jpg&h=57a052f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/all_nations/imgs/c/9/c9822179.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fall_nations%2Fimgs%2Fc%2F9%2Fc9822179.jpg&h=54e58513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/all_nations/imgs/e/0/e08e7c56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fall_nations%2Fimgs%2Fe%2F0%2Fe08e7c56.jpg&h=57a052f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/all_nations/imgs/e/0/e08e7c56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fall_nations%2Fimgs%2Fe%2F0%2Fe08e7c56.jpg&h=57a052f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要除中共 先誅李嘉誠</span></span></blockquote><br />\n香港同中國太近啦  係厚烈既華夏文化之下 <br />\n太容易受感染令人誤以為自己係中國人<br />\n其實果香港可以再大啲  或者同北方大陸有個緩衝點就會好好多"},{"pid":"2d354639e83a42315e96467aeca6c20483a7568a","tid":304231,"uid":82391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:47:34.000Z","msg":"歸英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b26eee0b553f50c961272a8da2de5289a002493","tid":304231,"uid":48659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/all_nations/imgs/e/0/e08e7c56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fall_nations%2Fimgs%2Fe%2F0%2Fe08e7c56.jpg&h=57a052f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/all_nations/imgs/c/9/c9822179.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fall_nations%2Fimgs%2Fc%2F9%2Fc9822179.jpg&h=54e58513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/all_nations/imgs/e/0/e08e7c56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fall_nations%2Fimgs%2Fe%2F0%2Fe08e7c56.jpg&h=57a052f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/all_nations/imgs/e/0/e08e7c56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fall_nations%2Fimgs%2Fe%2F0%2Fe08e7c56.jpg&h=57a052f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要除中共 先誅李嘉誠</span></span></blockquote><br />\n香港同中國太近啦  係厚烈既華夏文化之下 <br />\n太容易受感染令人誤以為自己係中國人<br />\n其實果香港可以再大啲  或者同北方大陸有個緩衝點就會好好多</blockquote><br />\n假設廣東省可以分離到出去  咁樣對香港都有好大幫助  因為大家都係嶺南文化  講粵語<br />\n咁樣就唔洗直接受北方政權直接既衝擊<br />\n根本香港人廣東人同其他省份既文化同特質都唔同<br />\n係歐洲黎睇 我地根本就係另一個民族黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e71ff75fce8f3545a33d9aa8a84112470895b34","tid":304231,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T18:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你自己覺得恥辱姐，唔好拉埋其他人講"},{"pid":"3514161f05b2601fe6ef31db962c33dc1fba087c","tid":304231,"uid":58358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T18:07:11.000Z","msg":"比利時同法國都係講法文，都要分做兩個國家，廣東話同北京話爭咁遠卻要夾硬統一"},{"pid":"13f74dd1f1f3df820b1699c27e7f2d6291ca060b","tid":304231,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T21:28:35.000Z","msg":","},{"pid":"8ad8a438e028962178e129c8d982b223c01b8378","tid":304231,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T21:29:36.000Z","msg":"移民"}]}